<ArticleLayout
  title="The Certainty Dealers"
  description="There is an industry built on your need for answers. It is enormous, it is growing, and it almost never sells you what it says it does. The product is not information. It is the feeling of resolution."
  category="Mental Health"
  readTime="20 min read"
